::Firearm::

Firearm smiles down at Feline. "Yup, us Maximals are kind!"

The two reach the CR room, Firearm grinning at Prowl and Iron Raptor, who 
were kissing in front of one of the CR chambers. He looks back at Feline, 
opening a chamber.

"You can use this one," Firearm says to her, "Just don't distract the 
lovebots over there."
